song_name: Straw Hat And Dirty Old Hank
Straw Hat And Old Dirty Hank

version_description: I always find myself adding/changing chords from what's available and have settled on this arrangement. There is a short set of intro chords. This version has C's before many of the Cadd9 chords, and several places where C replaces Cadd9. It has careful alignment with chord changes. The last line from the first chorus has a different chord progression than I've seen elsewhere.
